               <text>
                  <paragraph>Ascorbic Acid, Butylated Hydroxytoluene, Cetyl Alcohol, Edetate Disodium, Fragrance, Glycerin, Glycolic Acid, Methylparaben, Propylparaben, Purified Water, Sodium Lauryl Sulfate, Sodium Metabisulfite, Stearyl Alcohol, Vitamin E Acetate.</paragraph>
